      <p><a href="ch73s29.html#MonstersAnimals102">Mules</a> are sterile crossbreeds of donkeys and <a href="ch73s21.html#MonstersAnimals68">horses</a>. A <a href="ch73s29.html#MonstersAnimals102">mule</a> is similar to a light <a href="ch73s21.html#MonstersAnimals68">horse</a>, but slightly stronger and more agile.</p>
