          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Carrying Capacity:</strong></span> A light load for a <a href="ch73s29.html#MonstersAnimals102">mule</a> is up to 230 pounds; a medium load, 231-460 pounds; and a heavy load, 461-690 pounds. A <a href="ch73s29.html#MonstersAnimals102">mule</a> can drag 3,450 pounds.</p>
